{"tid":467230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(代友開post)我Ex差我錢唔撚還","createTime":"2017-11-13T10:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T15:42:51.000Z","uid":24610,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"910b7cc0ae6151da147d99ddf269fc83f99026da","tid":467230,"uid":24610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"事源2016年11月左右<br />\n我同我拍左拖6年既Ex分左手<br />\n分手原因係佢背住我偷食第2條女<br />\n之後仲要比我發現佢搞大左17歲女仔既肚<br />\n後尾仲要叫佢落左個仔<br />\n同佢拍拖個陣佢成日問我借錢 <br />\n又唔還<br />\n之前仲一齊緊既時候 佢都仲會每月還一兩千比我<br />\n但分手後一直都冇還<br />\n佢差我一萬左右<br />\n或者對於各位黎講唔算多<br />\n但係係我辛苦返parttime 搵返黎<br />\n我半工讀<br />\n仲返緊學 <br />\n我有搵過佢媽媽<br />\n但係得到既回應係好串咁話係我地既事<br />\n同埋我Ex成日都block 我whatsapp <br />\n我搵唔到佢。<br />\n事隔一年<br />\n佢都係未還錢比我...<br />\nd錢對我黎講真係好多好重要<br />\n希望各位幫手推post <br />\n叫佢還錢<br />\n唔該你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c93b0a5a2758f60ff465431b3c15b1c2c0b15c","tid":467230,"uid":89270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"9成追唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過幫推"},{"pid":"170ea1c32dffed8a658b0fa518021ae1a6144195","tid":467230,"uid":24610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9成追唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過幫推</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f79f1ba7aac27bac94ec574f196f0a1110e4c1","tid":467230,"uid":24610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"有圖 <br />\n我岩岩放學返緊去 <br />\